<html>
<head>
<title>Dance Scheduler Beta Test Cookie</title>
<style>
body {
    margin: 50px;
    max-width: 500px;
    padding: 50px;
    <% IF curr_val %>
        border: 20px double red;
    <% END %>
}

div {
    margin: 10px;
}

form {
    border: 1px solid black;
    padding: 10px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body >
<h2>Dance Scheduler Beta Test Cookie</h2>

<div>
    This manages a cookie that will let you preview the pages as generated by the
    new system. New pages will have a big red border around them.
</div>
<div>
    Check out:
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://bacds.org">the front page</a>
        <li><a href="https://www.bacds.org/series/contra/berkeley_wed/">the individual series pages</a>
        <li><a href="https://www.bacds.org/series/contra/berkeley_wed/?single-event=2023-02-02">the individual event pages</a>
        <li><a href="https://www.bacds.org/dancefinder/">the dancefinder</a>
        <li><a href="https://www.bacds.org/livecalendar.html">the live/interactive calendar</a>
        <li><a href="https://bacds.org/calendars/2022/09/">archive calendar pages</a>
    </ul>
</div>
<form method="POST">
    <div>
        <label for="off">off</label>
        <input type="radio" name="beta-cookie" value="off" <% IF !curr_val %>checked<% END %>>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for="on">on</label>
        <input type="radio" name="beta-cookie" value="on" <% IF curr_val %>checked<% END %>>
    </div>
    <input type="submit">
</form>
<div>
<a href="/">Return to homepage</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
